Business for Britain was launched in April with the intention of bringing the economy to the table and defining what those who provide prosperity and work in the UK want to change in our relations with the EU.
To this end, we have commissioned the largest and most comprehensive survey of UK economic leaders and asked them what they think about Britain, the economy and the EU.
YouGov surveyed more than 1,000 executives from the industry, representing around the UK’s corporate sizes, sectors and regions.
